Package: fritzbox-watchdog
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, iputils-ping, systemd
Maintainer: rgho <rohi@rgho.de>
Description: Automated FritzBox router restart when internet fails
 FritzBox Router Watchdog monitors internet connectivity and restarts
 your FritzBox router when connection fails. Simple systemd service
 with configurable thresholds and cooldown protection.
